{% comment %}
  Commerce Shield — Order Status / Thank-You Page Analytics Suppression

  HOW TO USE:
    Copy the <script> block below (not this comment) and paste it into:
    Shopify Admin → Settings → Checkout → scroll to "Order status page"
      → "Additional scripts" textarea → Save

  WHAT IT DOES:
    Loads the Commerce Shield pixel guard on the order status / thank-you page.
    Bots that bypassed the storefront and completed checkout directly will have
    their GA4 and Meta Pixel analytics suppressed here.

    Liquid variables ({{ }}) work inside "Additional scripts" so
    shop.permanent_domain resolves correctly at render time.
{% endcomment %}

<script>
(function() {
  var shop = {{ shop.permanent_domain | json }};
  var origin = 'https://commerce-shield-prod.ncassidy.workers.dev';
  var s = document.createElement('script');
  s.src = origin + '/cs-pixel-guard.js?shop=' + encodeURIComponent(shop) + '&enabled=1';
  s.async = true;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
})();
</script>
